2026-03-07 00:37:03.123 [boundedElastic-1] DEBUG c.i.m.t.service.TargetProcessService - Response status=200 body={"Items":[{"ResourceType":"UserStory","Id":203758,"Name":"Analyse S+ Insurance Integration","Description":"<!--markdown-->## WHY\nTo strengthen the value proposition of the Satispay Plus base plan, we will introduce the insurance benefit in Q1 2026. This marks the first step in expanding the Plus offering and integrating insurance services that can later be extended to additional plans.\n\n## WHAT\nThe objective of this request is to clarify the implementation details with the insurance provider.\n\nPlease take into account the following principles:\n\nNo opt-in required: consumers will be automatically enrolled in the insurance coverage as part of their Plus subscription.\nIn-app experience: within Satispay, users will only access general and useful information about the insurance service.\nExternal management: all detailed insurance flows, including the full UX, will be handled directly by the insurance provider outside the Satispay app.","CreateDate":"\/Date(1763984239000+0100)\/","Owner":{"ResourceType":"GeneralUser","Id":978,"Login":"aldo.lushkja@satispay.com"},"Project":{"ResourceType":"Project","Id":186131,"Name":"[IT-B] Satispay Plus"},"EntityState":{"ResourceType":"EntityState","Id":77,"Name":"Done"}},{"ResourceType":"UserStory","Id":203292,"Name":"Implement Outbox for SQS","Description":"<!--markdown--># WHY\n\nIn order to guarantee the **\"at least one\"** delivery behaviour while sending SQS messages and make it transactional with certain operation.\n\nMay happen that we have a domain model update in DB but we have no guarantee that SQS messages is delivered, so a recovery mechanism must be provided to handle this scenario.\n\n# WHAT\n\nImplement what have done with SNS using OutboxService also for SQS. \n\nIf schema table changes needed also provide a migration to insert in flyway directory.","CreateDate":"\/Date(1763544124000+0100)\/","Owner":{"ResourceType":"GeneralUser","Id":978,"Login":"aldo.lushkja@satispay.com"},"Project":{"ResourceType":"Project","Id":186131,"Name":"[IT-B] Satispay Plus"},"EntityState":{"ResourceType":"EntityState","Id":73,"Name":"Open"}}]}
